---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Qollect Help Center - User Manual"
  description="Qollect user guide covering setup, daily workflow, AI/OCR, LAN sync, privacy, and troubleshooting."
  lang="en"
>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-muted">Qollect Help Center</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-text-primary">Qollect User Manual</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-text-secondary leading-7">
          This guide is written for end users and focuses on practical daily usage. If you are new,
          start with <strong class="text-text-primary">Quick Start</strong> and
          <strong class="text-text-primary"> Core Workflow</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 glass-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">1. Quick Start (3 minutes)</h2>
      <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-text-secondary leading-7 list-decimal pl-5">
        <li>Download and install Qollect (Windows / macOS).</li>
        <li>On first launch, grant required system permissions if prompted.</li>
        <li>Open the main window with default shortcut: <code class="font-mono text-text-primary">Alt+X</code>.</li>
        <li>Copy a few texts/images and confirm they appear in history automatically.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">
        Tip: If your shortcut does not work, it is usually a conflict with OS/global tools. Change it in Settings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 glass-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">2. Core Workflow (recommended daily path)</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-7">
        <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Step A:</strong> Copy as usual, Qollect captures clipboard history in the background.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Step B:</strong> When needed, open Qollect and search by keyword, tag, or type.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Step C:</strong> Click an item to copy it back, or open its original file/link.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Step D:</strong> Pin important items to Workbench for long-term reuse.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 glass-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">3. Key Features</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3.1 Search & Filtering</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-7">Use full-text search, tags, and type filters to find content quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3.2 AI Tagging</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-7">After configuring an AI provider, Qollect can auto-tag entries for easier retrieval.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3.3 OCR</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-7">Extract text from images and make image-based content searchable.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3.4 View Modes</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-7">Switch between Mini, List, Panel, and Overview modes based on your task.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">3.5 Share & Sync</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary leading-7">Use QR sharing, temporary file hosts, and LAN sync for multi-device flow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 glass-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">4. Privacy & Data</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-text-secondary leading-7 list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Local-first by default. Core clipboard data is stored in local SQLite.</li>
        <li>Automatic cleanup policy can be configured by item count and max age.</li>
        <li>Import/export supports password-protected backups.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 glass-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">5. FAQ</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Q: Clipboard items are not showing up. What should I check?</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-text-secondary leading-7">A: Ensure Qollect is running, then check OS permissions and other clipboard utilities for conflicts.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Q: Shortcut is not working.</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-text-secondary leading-7">A: Most likely a global shortcut conflict. Change it in Settings to an unused key combination.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Q: AI/OCR failed.</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-text-secondary leading-7">A: Verify API key, network access, and provider quota. Try a backup provider/model if needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
      <div class="glass-card p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">Need more help?</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-1">Open an issue with your scenario so we can improve Qollect faster.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a class="btn-glow-outline text-sm" href={`${base}en#download`}>Back to Download</a>
          <a class="btn-glow text-sm" href="https://github.com/zongqir/qollect/issues" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open Issue</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
